_sText:
Thank you fps god for making the original surf_ambient_fixed <3 

A version of surf_ambient made to mimic the changes made on ksf.

The map includes trigger_multiples for hook zones under the names of:
timer_startzone
timer_checkpoint_1 to 4 
timer_endzone
otherwise they can just be used to show you where the zones are by typing "showtriggers_toggle" in console.

the download will include zones for momentum 0.8.7:
https://github.com/momentum-mod/game/releases
